认败选<ref>{{Cite web|title=GOP's Loeffler concedes to Warnock in Georgia runoff|url=https://apnews.com/article/joe-biden-johnny-isakson-georgia-media-jon-ossoff-5b120983d3f1e6adf9b0efe46a265ce8|accessdate=2021-01-13|date=2021-01-07|work=AP NEWS|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108025739/https://apnews.com/article/joe-biden-johnny-isakson-georgia-media-jon-ossoff-5b120983d3f1e6adf9b0efe46a265ce8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。沃诺克在就任后将成为美国参议院第一位代表前[[邦聯州|邦聯州]]的非裔民主党人。<ref>{{cite web|title=African American Senators|url=https://www.senate.gov/pagelayout/history/h_multi_sections_and_teasers/Photo_Exhibit_African_American_Senators.htm|publisher=United States Senate|access-date=January 6, 2021|archive-date=July 2, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702035451/https://www.senate.gov/pagelayout/history/h_multi_sections_and_teasers/Photo_Exhibit_African_American_Senators.htm}}</ref><ref>{{Cite newspaper|last=Thebault|first=Reis|last2=Scherer|first2=Michael|last3=Wootson|first3=Cleve R., Jr.|date=2021-01-05|title=Raphael Warnock wins Georgia runoff election against Sen. Loeffler, lifting Democratic hopes of claiming Senate majority|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/perdue-ossoff-loeffler-warnock-georgia-senate/2021/01/05/7d7b5afe-4f5d-11eb-83e3-322644d82356_story.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106141547/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/perdue-ossoff-loeffler-warnock-georgia-senate/2021/01/05/7d7b5afe-4f5d-11eb-83e3-322644d82356_story.html|archive-date=January 6, 2021|access-date=2021-01-06|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]}}: "Warnock will be the first African American Democratic senator from a former Confederate state" <!-- Quote added because was disputed multiple times by extended editors. --></ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Martin|last2=Fausset|first1=Jonathan|first2=Richard|date=January 6, 2021|title=Warnock Beats Loeffler in Georgia Senate Race|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/06/u