== 个人生活 ==
沃诺克在2016年2月14日所举行的公开仪式上与乌莱耶·恩多耶（Oulèye Ndoye）结婚。夫妻在一月份举行了私人婚礼。<ref name="wedding"/><ref name="wedding-2">{{Cite web|title=A look at the wedding of Rev. Raphael Warnock and Ouleye Ndoye|url=https://www.ajc.com/blog/arts-culture/look-the-wedding-rev-raphael-warnock-and-ouleye-ndoye/DZVd06KtJqEUo1rdiBaTPO/|accessdate=2020-02-01|author=Poole|date=2016-02-16|first=Shelia|publisher=The Atlanta Journal-Constitution|quote=The Rev. Raphael G. Warnock, senior pastor of Ebenezer Baptist Church, and Ouleye Ndoye were wed publicly on Valentine's Day at the Auburn Avenue church. They initially wed in a private ceremony last month in Danforth Chapel on the campus of Morehouse College, Warnock’s alma mater.|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106141527/https://www.ajc.com/blog/arts-culture/look-the-wedding-rev-raphael-warnock-and-ouleye-ndoye/DZVd06KtJqEUo1rdiBaTPO/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他们有两个孩子。夫妻两人于2019年11月分居，而他们于2020年离婚。<ref name="pulpit_to_senate_2020_11_01_nytimes_com"/>根据警方的报告，恩多耶指责沃诺克在试图逃避一场关于探亲的激烈争吵时，用他的车碾过她的脚，但体检人员没有发现受伤的迹象。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Warnock, wife involved in dispute|url=https://www.ajc.com/news/local-govt--politics/warnock-wife-involved-dispute/MCQYpvtswlZIIGdItrfcBJ/|accessdate=2020-03-10|author=Deere|date=2020-03-07|first=Stephen|work=The Atlanta Journal-Constitution|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106141515/https://www.ajc.com/news/local-govt--politics/warnock-wife-involved-dispute/MCQYpvtswlZIIGdItrfcBJ/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在第二轮选举前，警方在事发期间的执法记录仪影像被公开。<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-12-24|title=Warnock says he'll focus on Georgians after video of ex-wife surfaces|work=The Hill|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/state-watch/531629-warnock-responds-after-video-of-ex-wifes-accusations-surfaces-im-going|accessdate=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106141531/https://thehill.com/homenews/state-watch/531629-warnock-responds-after-video-of-ex-wifes-accusations-surfaces-im-going|dead-url=no}}</ref>

